items.name: SharpDX-Rastertek-Tutorials
items.description: This is a C# repository based off the Rastertek Tutorial Series posted on www.Rastertek.com, is a literal conversion of the C++ implementations posted on the WebSite, to a .NET C# based implementation using SharpDX 3.0.2, DirectX 11 & WinForms. This is intended for C# developers to use as a reference when trying to learn DirectX 11 3D programming, especially when most examples using DirectX are written in C++, so this repo is mimiking ALOT of common C++ DirectX style code writing but in your favorite language C#! So please unless you find an error its not intended for new contributions, its easy to run these tutorials as I have included a Winforms UI for executing every Tutorial example found on www.Rastertek.com. Enjoy!.

items.description: 3dpl (3D Programming Language), A language based on Unity3d's JS for new programmers to learn programming and 3D game programming at the same time, and while having fun! It includes 17 tutorials, which include how to make a simple cube how to color the cubes how to make 3D brakeout(arkanoid) and how to make a 3D space first person shooter. Also you can upload your programs to the (cloud server, still in development stage) and enjoy a huge library of programs made by other users!
